{
    "manually_checked": false,
    "poem_title": "A un girasol",
    "author": "Joaquín Arcadio Pagaza",
    "poem_alt_title": "Espejo de lealtad, flor admirable,",
    "corpus": "disco2_1",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": "1",
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "1",
                    "line_text": "Espejo de lealtad, flor admirable,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---++--+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "2",
                    "line_text": "que inmoble y a la par en movimiento",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "3",
                    "line_text": "saludando de Febo el nacimiento,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "4",
                    "line_text": "a su ocaso le sigues invariable.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+-++---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Espejo de lealtad, flor admirable,\nque inmoble y a la par en movimiento\nsaludando de Febo el nacimiento,\na su ocaso le sigues invariable."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "2",
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "5",
                    "line_text": "Es tan fino tu amor inimitable,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+++--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "6",
                    "line_text": "que si envuelto en su manto ceniciento",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "7",
                    "line_text": "esquivo se levanta y soñoliento,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "8",
                    "line_text": "a través le contemplas siempre amable.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--++-+-+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Es tan fino tu amor inimitable,\nque si envuelto en su manto ceniciento\nesquivo se levanta y soñoliento,\na través le contemplas siempre amable."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "3",
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "9",
                    "line_text": "Si al amante Jesús, mi sol divino,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "10",
                    "line_text": "que me busca y me acecha enamorado,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-++-++---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "11",
                    "line_text": "como tú al luminar amara fino,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+-+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si al amante Jesús, mi sol divino,\nque me busca y me acecha enamorado,\ncomo tú al luminar amara fino,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "4",
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "12",
                    "line_text": "no me helaría al verlo disfrazado,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++-+-++--+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "13",
                    "line_text": "con capuz ingenioso y peregrino",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "14",
                    "line_text": "esconderse de mí Sacramentado.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--++-+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "no me helaría al verlo disfrazado,\ncon capuz ingenioso y peregrino\nesconderse de mí Sacramentado."
        }
    ]
}